  sonata-1.1.1.ebuild:
  Update DESCRIPTION to match upstream homepage.

*sonata-1.1.1 (26 May 2007)

  26 May 2007; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> sonata-1.0.1.ebuild,
  +sonata-1.1.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. Bug #177751, ebuild tweaks by Sebastian <sebastian_ml at
  gmx.net>.

  15 Apr 2007; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> -sonata-0.9.ebuild,
  sonata-1.0.1.ebuild:
  Add tag and lyrics USE flags. Patch by Stephen Boyd <bebarino at gmail.com>
  in bug #171247. Removed 0.9 ebuild.

  20 Feb 2007; Markus Rothe <corsair@gentoo.org> sonata-1.0.1.ebuild:
  Added ~ppc64

*sonata-1.0.1 (18 Feb 2007)

  18 Feb 2007; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> +sonata-1.0.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. Bug #165327, by Ihar Hrachyshka <ihar.hrachyshka at gmail.com>.

  09 Jan 2007; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> sonata-0.9.ebuild:
  Use full atom for built_with_use.

  04 Dec 2006; <ticho@gentoo.org> -sonata-0.6.ebuild, -sonata-0.7.1.ebuild,
  -sonata-0.8.ebuild, -sonata-0.8.1.ebuild, sonata-0.9.ebuild:
  Warn user if GTK+ was built without jpeg USE flag. Warning suggested by
  Avuton Olrich <avuton at gmail.com>. Removed old ebuilds.

